channel.title: Omg please help me >>>>>.<<<<
channel.description:
I have been here 9 hours straight keep hitting refresh trying get someone to help me, but every time I ask a question people get on here and call each other idiots and retards and a bunch of crap instead of even paying attention to my question. I have 1 question and I really want someone to help. I don't know much about programming so I am a noob when it comes to this stuff. If you don't want to help then simple, hit the RED X in your top right corner and go eat a bag of chips. This is really getting ridiculous. So thank you for those who do help.
Question:
I join my server by logging in with: Server IP: 0.0.0.0 Port: 5555
I can logon but noone else can. I have read the probably about every guide on here. I have forwarded ALL my ports correctly. Disabled Firewalls. Disabled Anti-virus.
I am using pimpscape source (is there another one I should try?)
1. I run the compiler.bat 2. I run runserver.bat 3. I login on my server 4. Noone else can log on
